title: Why Tulsi Gabbard Left The Democrat Party
itunes:title: Why Tulsi Gabbard Left The Democrat Party
description:
Tulsi Gabbard spent 8 years in Congress as a Democrat. She endorsed Bernie Sanders for president. Now, she's on the campaign trail stumping for Kari Lake and Joe Kent. Tulsi joins Charlie for a whole episode to explain how warmongering, anti-white racism, and gender insanity pushed her out of the Democrat Party for good.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
